com.stripe.android

Class StripeIntentResult<T extends StripeIntent>

  • com.stripe.android.StripeIntentResult<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PaymentIntentResult, SetupIntentResult

    public class StripeIntentResult<T extends StripeIntent>

    A model representing the result of a interface StripeIntent confirmation or authentication attempt via Stripe.confirmPayment or Stripe.handleNextActionForPayment

    intent is a interface StripeIntent retrieved after confirmation/authentication succeeded or failed.

    See Also:
    interface StripeIntent, Stripe.confirmPayment, Stripe.handleNextActionForPayment, interface StripeIntent
